            class="border-b-2 border-white font-serif font-light leading-none transition hover:opacity-75"
            >Twenty(YC23)</a
          > — Contributed to the Twenty, helping improve Frontend related bugs and
          implementing core-team features.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/getsentry/sentry-javascript/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3Aharshit078+is%3Aclosed"
            class="border-b-2 border-white font-serif font-light leading-none transition hover:opacity-75"
            >SentryJS</a
