                    class="relative inline-block after:absolute after:bottom-[1px]
										after:left-1/2 after:z-[-1] after:h-1 after:w-full after:-translate-x-1/2
										after:border-b-[6px] after:border-[hsla(120,95%,59%,1)]"
                  >
                    Inagify
                  </span>
                  <ArrowUpRight class="size-4" />
                </span>
                <Image slot="img" src={inagify} alt="" />
              </Link>
            </h3>
            <p>
              - Inagify is a creative application that allows users to
              seamlessly add stylized text behind images and videos. Built with
              Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and Supabase, the platform offers a
              user-friendly interface for designers, content creators, and
              marketers to generate visually engaging content.
              <br />
